{"tid":414971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登有愛］一人一句支持連尼住 支持vip","createTime":"2017-09-26T15:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T18:24:40.000Z","uid":14719,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1219e82b881dd4e374a38d1e894e0f9bf746ecc5","tid":414971,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"估唔到早洩到今時今日都仲係咁不知悔改<br />\n向到縱容你班手下胡作非為<br />\n<br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<br />\n我地絕對相信連巴唔似得早洩咁卑鄙無恥<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 如果你肯一早為BAM HKG+而公開地躹躬道歉<br />\n根本就唔會搞到今時今日咁樣既局面<br />\n<br />\n到左今日高登再無高登仔係閣下咎由自取<br />\n你以為打殘LIHKG我地就會返返去你個垃圾高登只係你夢心妄想<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月出得第一個LIHKG <br />\n我地就有本事可以再出得到千千萬萬個LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都無謂<br />\n我地對連尼住同望遠兩位巴打係無條件信任<br />\n當中既情義係你依啲反覆無常既小人唔會明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之一句到尾<br />\n我就點都撐LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/kQgxJk/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FkQgxJk%2F2.jpg&h=e8b96282&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70e591e5647b77be89ea50911fc792670c5811c6","tid":414971,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/145507_978450a1b45ab82601476aa6d9468ebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F145507_978450a1b45ab82601476aa6d9468ebc.jpg&h=d42bf130&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c13fae3acc981ff7d303d83d6c3c356708192ad5","tid":414971,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/145507_978450a1b45ab82601476aa6d9468ebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F145507_978450a1b45ab82601476aa6d9468ebc.jpg&h=d42bf130&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴💪🏻"},{"pid":"72e09ab5792bbc4